<br>
I pull, a lot, and if i get a caster who, instead of pulling, decides to sit an nuke me.. cast bounce.  While the 200-1k damage their nukes do to themselves (still has not caused me to like being ice comet'd) might not seem like a lot, pulling multiples, and having one mez itself is priceless.<br>
<br>
The only caution is, is you're expecting a multiple pull.. do not cast it if there are necro mobs.... they do tend to lead with dots, and if it dot's itself... well, you know the rest. <p><!--EZCODE HR START--><hr /><!--EZCODE HR END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Moraganth Dreamweaver<br>
